<br>
10-14 or so, steamfont near mino caves.  pull drakes, skellies, harpies, elementals.  the drakes don't group.  Ok loot for this level, and they drop important racial temper components and mercury, (poison component?).<br>
<br>
prolly 8-12, tunnellers in paludal.  they don't group and they appear to be low resist.  Loot sucks.<br>
<br>
12-16 or so, fungal fiends, also paludal.  they group, but they are laid out such that you can single pull many of them.  Loot nominally better, but still poor.<br>
<br>
16-18 (not telling.  sorry.)<br>
<br>
18-20 sk hermit.  I used air pet, buff, ds, sent pet in, and nuked hard through the cabin walls.<br>
<br>
That's as far as I've gotten so far.  Debating my next step.  Maybe the rogue in the hk prison, Osargen.<br>
<br>
BTW, I'm trying to stick to killing low red or yellow almost exclusively.  I don't mind the downtime, and I'm running several other chars through a similar path, though the mage is the only one who can solo red consistently.<br>
<br>
Aanni - mage20, (other chars levels 54, 33, 23, 22, 16, 15, 15, 13, ...)<br>
